  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1452020/extras/3d52ef10ec73f0d2293a71b02642d9a3.avif?t=1726751590\" width=616 height=200 /></span><br><strong><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >This game is all about you approaching cute girls, not about matching other girls up!</h2></strong><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>This is a puzzle game, it's hard.</strong></h2>You're a girl who likes girls, walking into this Yuri dating agency to find yourself a date.<br>Here, you will be able to get to know lots of girls, including a genius scientist, a filthy rich vampire, a cute apple, and more! Although they all want to find a girlfriend, it will still be anything but easy for you to get the ball rolling with them.<br>Will you be able to win their hearts? Or will you get a reality check then continue to live a miserable single life?<br><br>Key Features:<br>This is a speed dating simulator. Players will play as \"I/me\", the protagonist in the game and get to date with more than 7 characters.<br>Some hidden lore will be discovered as the story progresses. After dating the characters, players will acquire the knowledge of the hidden details of each character.<br>This game contains a large number of choices, and each option will lead to different endings.<br>Enjoy all the possible choices in dates and the background stories coming with them!<br><br>Highlights:<br>⭐  <strong>Experience lesbian dating in the first person experience</strong><br>⭐ >7 Characters to Date + 2 pairs to set up<br>⭐ > 20 Steam Achievements <br>⭐ > 25 CGs<br>⭐ Interactive Choices<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1452020/extras/ac9fdbc27397d7132c303d716bad6e0b.avif?t=1726751590\" width=140 height=140 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam